---
title: Double Honey Chermoula Lamb Rump with Roast Root Veggie Toss & Yoghurt
description: Chermoula spices are the ideal seasoning to complement lamb, and with a hearty roast veggie toss plus a side of creamy yoghurt, there's a burst of flavour in every bite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6617a1f1300be64307bdf78e-52650015.jpeg
